r>
<br>
Frankly, I think that the possiblitly to do this is @#%$, and needs to be fixed immediately. I didn't petition it because I didn't want friends of mine to get into trouble, but it still needs to be fixed ASAP.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thehawnz>the hawnz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://images.fotki.com/v13/photos/4/41603/158712/noble-vi.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 71<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/5/02 9:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: CHEAT your way to PoV (cross post)</span><hr size=1> why does it need to be fixed?  it's like the only guaranteed way to farm keys for your guildies.  a group with a druid shaman monk chanter cleric and warrior certainly has no chance of winning, so you'd have a lot of keys just rot because you have to take at least some DPS with you every time.  easy way to fix this is just to destroy the extra marks on the corpse if you don't want anyone else looting them.  problem solved. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=raaj>Raaj</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 544<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/5/02 10:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: CHEAT your way to PoV (cross post)</span><hr size=1> It needs to be fixed because it's cheap.<br>
<br>
It's not as if the executioner is all that hard, if they need to cheat to get into valor, they have no business being there. The same goes for guilds that are winning with the same group again and again and farming the marks for people without enough intelligence to do it themselves. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=331173" target="top">Raaj</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.clantaveren.com" target="top">Clan Ta Veren</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
