<br>
It's a 2 minutes recast, and the mobs can/will resist it. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Vermyn V'Grymm</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
